    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: Guidance for managing playgrounds and outdoor gyms
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for owners and operators of playgrounds and outdoor gyms to enable their use while minimising the transmission risk of coronavirus (COVID-19).

</p>

  </div>
</div>

